---
import Layout from '../../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const title = "Montenegro Citizenship by Investment Guide 2025";
const description = "Complete guide to Montenegro's CBI program for EU candidate country. €350,000+ investment requirement, potential EU pathway, insurance requirements, and healthcare access in the Adriatic.";

const schema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": title,
  "description": description,
  "author": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "Compare Expat Plans"
  },
  "datePublished": "2025-01-15",
  "dateModified": "2025-01-15"
};
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />

  <PageShell
    title={title}
    subtitle="Your complete guide to citizenship by investment in Montenegro"
    heroImage="/images/countries/montenegro-hero-bg.png"
  >
    <!-- Quick Facts Box -->
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">Montenegro CBI: Quick Facts</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Total Investment:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> €350,000-€450,000+</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Processing Time:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> 3-6 months</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Program Status:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> Limited applications (winding down)</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">EU Status:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> Candidate country (target 2028-2030)</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Visa-Free Countries:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> 124+ (Schengen area included)</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-semibold text-neutral-700">Insurance Requirement:</span>
          <span class="text-neutral-900"> Required for application</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Program Status Alert -->
    <div class="bg-amber-50 border-2 border-amber-400 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">⚠️ Important: Program Status</h3>
      <p class="text-amber-900">
        Montenegro's CBI program was launched in 2019 with limited spots and is being phased out as the country
        prepares for EU membership. The program originally accepted only 2,000 applications and is now in its final
        phase. If you're interested, act quickly—applications may close permanently at any time. Verify current
        availability with licensed agents before beginning the process.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <section id="overview" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Overview</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        Montenegro's Citizenship by Investment Program offers a unique opportunity: citizenship in an EU candidate
        country that's actively negotiating accession. While not yet an EU member, Montenegro has opened and closed
        multiple chapters of the EU acquis and targets membership around 2028-2030. If Montenegro joins the EU,
        citizens would gain automatic EU citizenship rights—free movement, work, and residence throughout the
        27-nation bloc.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        The program requires substantial investment: €350,000-€450,000 in approved development projects (depending
        on location) plus a €100,000 donation to the government development fund. Unlike Caribbean programs focused
        purely on second passports, Montenegro's CBI is tied to real estate development in specific regions, creating
        an asset with potential appreciation.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        Healthcare in Montenegro is developing—Podgorica and coastal areas have adequate facilities, but complex
        care typically requires evacuation to Belgrade, Zagreb, or Vienna. International health insurance with
        evacuation coverage is essential. The mandatory insurance requirement for the application process ensures
        basic coverage, but comprehensive plans are strongly recommended.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Quick Decision Guide -->
    <section id="decision-guide" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Quick Decision Guide</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-3">Montenegro CBI is Ideal If You:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-900">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Want potential future EU citizenship (upon Montenegro's accession)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Prefer real estate investment over non-refundable donations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Value Schengen zone visa-free access (already available)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Are interested in the Adriatic/Mediterranean lifestyle</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Can act quickly (limited applications remaining)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-3">Consider Alternatives If You:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-amber-900">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Need guaranteed EU citizenship (uncertain timeline)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Want lower investment cost (Caribbean options from $100K)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Prefer faster, more established programs (St. Kitts since 1984)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Need US E-2 Treaty access (Grenada is better)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Require excellent local healthcare (limited facilities)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Official Requirements -->
    <section id="requirements" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Official Requirements</h2>

      <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Investment Structure</h3>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Component 1: Development Project Investment</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-2">
              Investment in an approved development project in designated regions. The project must be pre-approved
              by the government and typically involves tourism or hospitality development.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Northern Montenegro (underdeveloped areas): €250,000 minimum</li>
              <li>• Coastal/Southern Montenegro (developed areas): €450,000 minimum</li>
              <li>• Projects include: Hotels, resorts, tourism infrastructure</li>
              <li>• Must remain invested for at least 5 years</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900">Component 2: Government Donation</h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-2">
              Non-refundable contribution to the government development fund, supporting national infrastructure
              and development programs.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-neutral-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Fixed amount: €100,000</li>
              <li>• Required regardless of investment location</li>
              <li>• Non-refundable contribution</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Total Investment Summary</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-1 text-blue-900 text-sm">
            <li>• <strong>Northern Montenegro:</strong> €250,000 + €100,000 = €350,000 minimum</li>
            <li>• <strong>Coastal Montenegro:</strong> €450,000 + €100,000 = €550,000 minimum</li>
            <li>• Plus: Processing fees, due diligence, legal costs (~€40,000-€60,000)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Eligibility Criteria</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Age:</strong> Main applicant must be 18 years or older</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Clean record:</strong> No criminal convictions, not subject to international sanctions</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Source of funds:</strong> Legally acquired, properly documented</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Health insurance:</strong> Valid coverage in Montenegro required</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Dependents:</strong> Spouse, children under 18, children 18-26 if in education</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Nationality restrictions:</strong> Citizens of certain countries may face additional scrutiny</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Required Documents</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">1.</span>
            <span>Completed application forms</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">2.</span>
            <span>Valid passport (certified copy, all pages)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">3.</span>
            <span>Birth certificate (apostilled, translated to Montenegrin)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">4.</span>
            <span>Marriage certificate if applicable (apostilled, translated)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">5.</span>
            <span>Police clearance from country of citizenship and residence</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">6.</span>
            <span>Medical certificate confirming good health</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">7.</span>
            <span>Proof of source of funds (bank statements, business records)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">8.</span>
            <span>CV/resume</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">9.</span>
            <span>Proof of investment commitment (reservation agreement)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">10.</span>
            <span>Health insurance certificate valid in Montenegro</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary-600 font-bold">11.</span>
            <span>4 passport photos per applicant</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Insurance Requirements -->
    <section id="insurance-requirements" class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Insurance Requirements</h2>

      <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-2">Health Insurance Mandatory</h3>
        <p class="text-amber-900">
          Montenegro requires valid health insurance coverage as part of the CBI application. The insurance must
          be valid in Montenegro and cover medical expenses. While specific minimums aren't always stated, comprehensive
          international health insurance with evacuation coverage is strongly recommended given Montenegro's limited
          healthcare infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
        <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Recommended Coverage</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Annual maximum: €500,000+ recommended</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Medical evacuation to EU (essential)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Coverage valid in Montenegro and Balkans</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>24/7 emergency assistance</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Why Evacuation is Critical</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Only one major hospital (Clinical Centre Montenegro)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Limited specialist care available</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Belgrade evacuation: 1 hour by air</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Vienna/Zagreb for major procedures</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Insurance After Citizenship</h3>
        <p class="text-blue-900 mb-4">
          Once you become a Montenegrin citizen, you're eligible for the public healthcare system (FZOM). However,
          for complex care and international coverage:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-blue-900">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
            <span><strong>Resident:</strong> FZOM + private international insurance recommended</span>
          </li>
